主要翻译
 
flame n (fire)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 火焰 huǒ yàn TC Traditional Chinese 火焰  
 -- The candle's flame flickered.
 -- 蜡烛上的火焰跳动着。
 
flames npl (fire)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 火焰 huǒ yàn TC Traditional Chinese 火焰  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 焰火 huǒ yàn，yàn huǒ 
 -- Welcoming flames flickered in the hearth.
 -- 壁炉中的焰火跳动着，好似在欢迎谁。
 
flame [sb] ▦ vtr informal (attack: fellow internet user)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 挑战 tiǎo zhàn TC Traditional Chinese 挑戰  (互联网，以激怒为目的)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 挑衅 tiǎo zhàn，tiǎo xìn TC Traditional Chinese 挑釁 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 煽动 tiǎo zhàn，shān dòng TC Traditional Chinese 煽動 
 -- The gamer challenged another player who was flaming him to a duel.
 -- 那位玩家向挑衅自己的另一位玩家发出了决斗挑战。

其他翻译
 
flame n informal (attack posted on internet)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 挑衅性言论 tiǎo xìn xìng yán lùn  (互联网)
 -- I received hundreds of flames after I posted my message on the forum.
 -- 在论坛上发贴后，我收到了数百条挑衅性言论。
 
flame ▦ vi (burn, blaze)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 焚烧 fén shāo TC Traditional Chinese 焚燒  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 燃烧 fén shāo，rán shāo TC Traditional Chinese 燃燒 
 -- The campfire flamed when the breeze started blowing.
 
flame vi (glow)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 闪耀 shǎn yào  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 发光 shǎn yào，fā guāng TC Traditional Chinese 發光 
 -- A soft light flamed in the distance.

复合形式： 
 
burst into flame, burst into flames v expr informal (catch fire)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 猛烈燃烧起来 měng liè rán shāo qǐ lái  
 -- The bus burst into flames, trapping the passengers inside.
 
flame-retardant adj (fire resistant)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 阻燃的 zǔ rán de  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 防火的 zǔ rán de，fáng huǒ de 
 
flame retardant n (fire resistance)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 阻燃剂  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 防火材料 
 
old flame n informal, figurative (ex-lover)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 旧情人  
 -- Ron hooked up with an old flame after his girlfriend dumped him.

